This is a great recipe for pea soup. I've already made it several times and its a great staple recipe. For the user who made it with turkey kielbasa - I agree it DOES NOT WORK with turkey - my soup came out bland and nothing special. Definitely use a GOOD pork kielbasa and I've also used a large ham bone before. I followed the recipe to a T the first time and it was great - I've also done it with carrots which are a great addition. I would definitely make this again and again!

